                      @group(0) @binding(0) var<uniform> ubuf: {ty};
                      @group(0) @binding(1) var<storage> sbuf: {ty};"),
            Ok(_module)
        }
    }

    // Host-shareable but not constructible types.
    let types = "atomic<i32> atomic<u32>
